","text":"]. (TA.) You say also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalN xiyaArN","text_ar":"جَمَلٌ خِيَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotaArN","text_ar":"مُخْتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A choice he-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAqapN","text_ar":"نَاقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaArN","text_ar":"خِيَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotaArapN","text_ar":"مُخْتَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A choice she-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyarapN","text_ar":"خِيَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] The dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxotaArN","text_ar":"مُخْتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxay~irN","text_ar":"مُخَيِّرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"is thrown out because it is augmentative; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it was changed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxtAr","text_ar":"مختار"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) one should not say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muxayotiyrN","text_ar":"مُخَيْتِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (El-Hareeree's Durrat el-Ghowwás, in De Sacy's Anthol. Gr. Ar. p. 49 of the Arabic text.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiyaArN","text_ar":"خِيَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S"]}]}}